tton\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-feedback\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-feedback\"></use></svg><span class=\"zDocsFeedbackButtonText\"> Feedback</span></span></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><button aria-label=\"Show topic actions\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" id=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-ellipsis-h\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-ellipsis-h\"></use></svg></button><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu zDocsTopicActionsMobileDropdown dropdown-menu-right\"></div></div><div style=\"flex-basis: 100%; height: 0px;\"></div><ul class=\"zDocsTopicPageDetails\"><li class=\"zDocsTopicPageDate css-cinqea\">Last Updated<span class=\"css-cinqea\">Okt 10, 2024</span></li><li class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryDetailsItem\"><button class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryButton\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-topic-summary\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-topic-summary\"></use></svg>Summarize</button></li><li class=\"spacer\" role=\"presentation\"></li><div class=\"zDocsLabelWrapper\"><ul><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: Uniface\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=prod_uniface\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>Uniface</a></li><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: 10.4\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=uniface_10.4\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>10.4</a></li></ul></div></ul></header><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBody\" data-prismjs-copy=\"Copy\" data-prismjs-copy-error=\"Copy failed! Use Ctrl + C instead.\" data-prismjs-copy-success=\"Copied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent wide\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104bbb1665702630169.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/bbb1665702630169.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/bbb1665702630169.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"bbb1665702630169\" role=\"article\">\n<h1 class=\"title topictitle1\" id=\"ariaid-title1\">\n      Force Fit\n </h1>\n<div class=\"body refbody\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">Force list items to be no higher than one character cell. By default, the height of list items is adjusted to accommodate the selected font.\n </p>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"bbb1665702630169__section_w839ab1b5b1_w840ab1b5_w841ab1\">\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table class=\"table\" count-columns=\"2\" id=\"bbb1665702630169__table_d12257e1_d12258e1_d12259e1\"><caption></caption><colgroup><col/><col/></colgroup><thead class=\"thead\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"bbb1665702630169__table_d12257e1_d12258e1_d12259e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">Value</p>\n</th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"bbb1665702630169__table_d12257e1_d12258e1_d12259e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">Description</p>\n</th>\n</tr>\n</thead><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"bbb1665702630169__table_d12257e1_d12258e1_d12259e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph defvalue\">False</code> (default)</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"bbb1665702630169__table_d12257e1_d12258e1_d12259e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">The height of list items is adjusted to accommodate the selected font.</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"bbb1665702630169__table_d12257e1_d12258e1_d12259e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">True</code>\n</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"bbb1665702630169__table_d12257e1_d12258e1_d12259e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">Each item in the list is displayed no higher than a one-character cell.</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"bbb1665702630169__section_uvv_npn_wwb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d191330e121\">Description</h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"bbb1665702630169__p_d103721e1_d103722e1_d103723e1\">This property cannot be set in ProcScript.</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"bbb1665702630169__section_qfv_4pn_wwb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d191330e130\">Applies To</h2>\n<ul class=\"ul\" id=\"bbb1665702630169__ul_o51_qpn_wwb\">\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"bbb1665702630169__li_d42221e1_d42222e1_d42223e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"vmo1688449724415.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/vmo1688449724415.html\" title=\"The ucombobox widget combines an input field with a drop-down list. It allows users to select one item from a previously defined list, or enter their own data instead. It is applicable only to form components. Uniface provides a logical widget called ComboBox, which is mapped to ucombobox.\">ucombobox (Combo Box)</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"bbb1665702630169__li_d42224e1_d42225e1_d42226e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"fud1688450548955.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/fud1688450548955.html\" title=\"The udropdownlist widget is a field-level widget that can display a list of valid options in a list below the input field, so that the user can select one. It is applicable only to form components.\">udropdownlist (DropDownList)</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"bbb1665702630169__li_d42227e1_d42228e1_d42229e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"rez1688451198680.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/rez1688451198680.html\" title=\"The ulistbox widget is a field-level widget that displays an open list in which one or more values can be selected. It can only be used in form components.\">ulistbox (ListBox )</a>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_3612051\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_3612051\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "Force Fit Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated Okt 10, 2024 Summarize Uniface 10.4 Force Fit Force list items to be no higher than one character cell. By default, the height of list items is adjusted to accommodate the selected font. Value Description False (default) The height of list items is adjusted to accommodate the selected font. True Each item in the list is displayed no higher than a one-character cell. Description This property cannot be set in ProcScript. Applies To ucombobox (Combo Box) udropdownlist (DropDownList) ulistbox (ListBox ) Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}